long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the thrilling world of Valorant with the Cypher X Omen X Sova live wallpaper Chrome extension. Perfect for Valorant fans, this chrome live wallpaper highlights the tactical prowess and unique skills of three iconic agents—Cypher, Omen, and Sova. Each new tab immerses you in the game’s intense atmosphere with vibrant visuals of these fan-favorite characters, ideal for players who appreciate the strategic gameplay and design of Valorant.

Key features include:

🎮 Live Wallpaper: Stunning graphics featuring Cypher, Omen, and Sova in action
🕒 Clock and Date Display: Game-inspired clock for a streamlined look
🔍 Google Search Bar: Quick searches from your new tab
🔗 Customizable Shortcuts: Arrange your top sites for fast navigation
Channel the essence of Valorant’s tactical edge every time you open a new tab, and keep your favorite agents just a click away.
